[assistant] `tests/src/com.diffplug.spotless/spotless-maven-plugin/2.43.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_spotless/spotless_maven_plugin/SpotlessMavenPluginTest.java`
[assistant] 
[assistant] What changed:
[assistant] - Removed use of `DefaultResourceManager`.
